reviewText: Not bad if you want to know about the Chinese Shar-Pei from the American Kennel Club's (AKC) point of view, in regards to showing this breed.  I knew this video was produced by the AKC; however, I thought there would be more on the breed from a holistic point of view, not just on showing.  Overall, it's okay, but I would recommend a pass, unless someone is interested in showing this breed.
